  <brief_title>Study About Effect of Preoperative Bowel Preparation Versus no Bowel Preparation Before Spinal Surgery</brief_title>
  <official_title>Preoperative Bowel Preparation Versus no Preparation Before Spinal Surgery: a Randomised Clinical Trial</official_title>
  <sponsors>
